overview: When aspiring influencer, Gemma Jordan, is taken down by an online troll, aka @therealgemmajordan, she sets out on a cross-country mission to confront them. But an internet troll isn’t the only thing that Gemma must come to face…  Commissioned by UNL Opera, THE REAL GEMMA JORDAN is a new musical film with a score by award-winning Broadway composer/lyricist Rob Rokicki and celebrated screenwriter Anna K. Jacobs. Directed by Alisa Belflower and Alexander Jeffrey, the musical film features a cast of UNL students with guest artists.
tagline: You deserve the best version of you
title: The Real Gemma Jordan
